# Reviewed exceptions and precedence
#
# This file documents the exception boundary; it is not a bypass list.
#
# Precedence:
# 1. Platform and user safety constraints.
# 2. Root and nearest AGENTS.md instructions.
# 3. More-specific command rules.
# 4. These reviewed repository exceptions.
#
# Exceptions must remain narrow, read-only where possible, and justified by
# the current task. Do not add an exception to avoid approval, validation, or
# an explicit user authorization requirement.

